cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.DS

This paper is likely to belong to the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it focuses on the training and performance of deep neural networks. It may also belong to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it deals with neural networks. Additionally, since the paper involves experiments on a video classification dataset, it may also belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision). The paper also proposes techniques for training and initialization, which may fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, since the paper involves a theoretical analysis of the expressivity of the networks, it may also belong to cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
